P(C)=1\times\frac{1}4+\frac{1}4\times0+\frac{1}2\times\frac{1}4=\frac{3}8
P(H_1|C)= \frac{P(C \bigcap H_1)}{P(C)}=\frac{P(C|H_1)P(H_1)}{P(C)}=\frac{1\times\frac{1}4}{\frac{3}8}=\frac{2}3
P(R|C)
P(R|C)= \frac{P(C \bigcap R)}{P(C)}=\frac{P(C|R)P(R)}{P(C)}
